documentation.name: Maintain the interior appearance of the SVG. The branded portion of the payment icon as provided meets the brand guidelines of the payment provider. Maintain the border property of the payment icon. It is designed to adapt to merchant branding in Checkout and payments and ensures a consistent appearance across the customer experience. The icon size is designed to be displayed consistently across checkout.
documentation.path: 游릭 Icons  > Payment Method > Maintain the interior appearance of the SVG. The branded portion of the payment icon as provided meets the brand guidelines of the payment provider. Maintain the border property of the payment icon. It is designed to adapt to merchant branding in Checkout and payments and ensures a consistent appearance across the customer experience. The icon size is designed to be displayed consistently across checkout.
